{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Q &#038; A Studio Ghibli: Transfer Knowledge, Film Baru, Sampai Disney","content":"<p>Acara konferensi pers Studio Ghibli kemarin (30/3) di Ritz Carlton Pacific Place rupanya cukup seru. Pasalnya pihak Studio Ghibli sendiri juga membawakan beberapa kabar yang menarik untuk disimak.</p>\n<p><strong>Film Baru</strong></p>\n<p>Toshio Suzuki selaku Direktur Eksekutif Studio Ghibli menerima pertanyaan terkait pengumuman pensiun Hayao Miyazaki. Miyazaki sendiri mengumumkan hendak pensiun di tahun 2013, namun setelah itu ia dikabarkan kembali membuat film sekali lagi untuk Studio Ghibli.</p>\n<p>“[Miyazaki-san] sekarang sedang berjuang sangat keras di Tokyo untuk membuat film baru,” jawab Suzuki-san dibantu dengan penerjemah. “Kami mengharap doa dari kalian semua agar film baru ini selesai.”</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1785\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1785\" data-attachment-id=\"1785\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/attachment/body-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-7\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Asian Movie Pulse&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1785\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Asian Movie Pulse\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1785\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Asian Movie Pulse</p></div></p>\n<p>Dikatakannya pula, saat ini Hayao Miyazaki sedang berfokus dalam tahap storyboarding. Ganbatte ne, Miyazaki-san!</p>\n<p><strong>Transfer Knowledge</strong></p>\n<p>Dengan diselenggarakannya acara The World of Ghibli Jakarta, tentu ada banyak kesempatan emas bagi pelaku industri kreatif di Indonesia untuk belajar secara langsung dari studio animasi Jepang yang telah memenangkan banyak penghargaan ini. Sayangnya, <em>transfer knowledge</em> yang sesungguhnya dari Studio Ghibli masih sangat terbatas untuk sekarang. Willawati, CEO dari Kaninga Pictures, mengatakan bahwa pihaknya masih berfokus untuk hal yang di depan mata terlebih dahulu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1786\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1786\" data-attachment-id=\"1786\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/attachment/body-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-8\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1786\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Urban News ID\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1786\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Urban News ID</p></div></p>\n<p>“Kita akan fokus dulu untuk mewujudkan The World of Ghibli Jakarta dengan sungguh-sungguh dan sepenuh-penuhnya,” kata Willawati. “Untuk meminta lebih dari ini saja kepada Studio Ghibli saya merasa sungkan.”</p>\n<p>Tapi, katanya, hal ini tidak menutup kemungkinan untuk kerja sama lainnya di masa depan. Untuk saat ini sih, anak muda di Indonesia berkesempatan jadi voluntir acara The World of Ghibli Jakarta dulu. <em>Alon-alon asal kelakon</em>, gitu.</p>\n<p><strong>Live Action Ghibli?!</strong></p>\n<p>Apakah Studio Ghibli tidak tertarik untuk membuat film live action yang mirip seperti yang dilakukan oleh Disney sekarang? Dengan hype yang tinggi untuk film-film seperti Beauty and the Beast, mungkin saja hal ini akan berakibat positif untuk studio Ghibli.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1787\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1787\" data-attachment-id=\"1787\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/attachment/body-9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"body-9\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1787\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: teen.co.id\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/body-9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1787\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: teen.co.id</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk yang satu ini, jawaban dari Toshio Suzuki cukup singkat. “Tidak,” katanya.</p>\n<p>Ia menyambung bahwa Studio Ghibli adalah studio animasi, dan tidak pernah terpikir untuk membuat film live action. “Mungkin Disney sudah kehabisan ide untuk membuat film animasi yang baru, jadi itu kenapa mereka membuat film live action,” tambahnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_1788\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1788\" data-attachment-id=\"1788\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/q-studio-ghibli-transfer-knowledge-film-baru-sampai-disney/attachment/gambar-2-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"gambar-2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Burn!! Photo by Zimbio&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1788\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Burn!! Photo by Zimbio\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/gambar-2-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-1788\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Burn!! Photo by Zimbio</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c224ae90-723a-51c5-9d19-d17810491ca6"}}}